# Generated by tauri-build on every compile: per-platform JSON schemas for
# capability-file autocompletion. Not build inputs — regenerated each build,
# and they vary by OS/toolchain (linux-/desktop-/windows-schema.json, CRLF on
# Windows), so tracking them just creates churn. Matches the standard Tauri
# scaffold's .gitignore.
/gen/schemas/
